children.subject: Poster of this comment, is there a way I can email you about 186? (I'm not the original poster of this post)

If you need to take another tech next semester alongside 61c and 170, from your current workload (I'm taking similar-workload classes and also don't have much of a social life so I can relate), I would recommend w186 over 164. Anecdotally I've heard that 164 is a lot of work even with Sen and afaik you need 61c (?) as a prereq so it might take some time to catch up to par with the coursework. I did take 186 last semester before 61c, so I can say the class material was manageable even without the unofficial 61c prereq. I personally wouldn't really want to take 2 difficult and 1 moderate (this is my personal judgment) techs in a semester, but w186 would be less work than 164 in any case.
Don't do a 3rd tech. Do 12-13 units only.

history.content:
Hi y'all,

This semester I'm taking 61b, 16b, 188, upper div H\SS and 195 and find it to be pretty busy (doing ok but no social life). 

Next fall I'll definitely take 61c and 170, and I'm contemplating a third tech.

Will 164 or w186 be manageable?
